{{> menu id="about"}}

<section class="ui left aligned middle aligned segment" style="padding: 2rem; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; font-family: sans-serif;">

  <h1>About Us</h1>
  <p>
    <strong>Welcome to the Playlist App!</strong> We’re here to help you organize and enjoy your music with ease. Whether you’re creating a playlist for a workout, a party, or just your daily vibe, we’ve got you covered.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>What We Do:</strong><br>
    The Playlist App makes it easy to create, manage, and share playlists. Discover new music, add your favorites, and enjoy them all in one place.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Features:</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>Create and organize playlists</li>
      <li>Discover new music</li>
      <li>Share your playlists with friends</li>
      <li>Sync across all your devices</li>
    </ul>
  </p>
  <p>
    We believe music should be simple, personal, and fun. Thanks for choosing the Playlist App!
  </p>

  <hr style="margin: 2rem 0;">

  <h2 class="ui header">App Statistics</h2>
  <p>The playlist app now contains:</p>

  <div class="ui center aligned grid" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
    <div class="eight wide column">
      <div class="ui five statistics">

        <div class="statistic">
          <div class="value" style="font-size: 2.5rem;">
            <i class="microphone icon" style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"></i><br>
            {{displayNumPlaylists}}
          </div>
          <div class="label" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
            Playlists
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="statistic">
          <div class="value" style="font-size: 2.5rem;">
            <i class="music icon" style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"></i><br>
            {{displayNumSongs}}
          </div>
          <div class="label" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
            Songs
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="statistic">
          <div class="value" style="font-size: 2.5rem;">
            <i class="chart bar outline icon" style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"></i><br>
            {{averageSongs}}
          </div>
          <div class="label" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
            Avg / Playlist
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="statistic">
          <div class="value" style="font-size: 2.5rem;">
            <i class="list ul icon" style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"></i><br>
            {{largestPlaylistTitle}}
          </div>
          <div class="label" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
            Largest
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="statistic">
          <div class="value" style="font-size: 2.5rem;">
            <i class="list ol icon" style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"></i><br>
            {{smallestPlaylistTitle}}
          </div>
          <div class="label" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
            Smallest
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>
